WEBVTT

00:16:29.741 --> 00:16:32.161
cho người nào đó"

00:16:32.161 --> 00:16:33.526
Vậy nên, giải thưởng TED mong ước

00:16:33.526 --> 00:16:34.686
của tôi là một phần hòa vốn,

00:16:34.686 --> 00:16:36.296
cộng với lãi suất.

00:16:36.296 --> 00:16:37.550
(cười)

00:16:37.574 --> 00:16:40.771
cho sự hào phóng và hảo tâm

00:16:40.771 --> 00:16:43.771
của con người.

00:16:43.771 --> 00:16:44.976
Tôi có một mong ước,

00:16:45.835 --> 00:16:48.526
Tôi mong chúng ta sẽ tìm ra được

00:16:48.526 --> 00:16:49.526
hàng triệu nơi khảo cổ

00:16:49.526 --> 00:16:51.526
chưa được biết đến

00:16:51.526 --> 00:16:53.137
trên khắp thế giới.

00:16:53.161 --> 00:16:54.623
Bằng việc tạo ra một đội ngũ

00:16:54.623 --> 00:16:57.433
thám hiểm của thế kỉ 21

00:16:57.623 --> 00:16:58.993
chúng ta sẽ tìm ra và bảo vệ di sản

00:16:59.053 --> 00:17:00.667
